        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[《公司作息时间表 WorkingTime》那个项目，用一句不客气的话说：表格不能下载，文字不能复制，部分内容瞬间消失，增删改无任何操作记录；项目责任人的自由度极大...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<br>《公司作息时间表 WorkingTime》那个项目，用一句不客气的话说：表格不能下载，文字不能复制，部分内容瞬间消失，增删改无任何操作记录；项目责任人的自由度极大，其他协作人的限制极多，数据的真实性极低，issues几乎从不处理；内容被删的概率极高。<br><br>这算什么开源？<br><br>再透露一点：这个项目的发起人，对GitHub的日常操作完全不熟悉。他自己的手机号在GitHub上暴露了他都浑然不知。贻笑大方！<br><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FmuPJwUrvwzi-1m_1qZX15arguB-v2.jpeg/strip/format/webp" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FmuPJwUrvwzi-1m_1qZX15arguB-v2.jpeg" type="image/jpeg"><img referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.jellow.site/FmuPJwUrvwzi-1m_1qZX15arguB-v2.jpeg"></picture><br><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/Fmhf8Y8NHkbj2cjt3Wy8u--yL-vYv2.jpeg/strip/format/webp" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/Fmhf8Y8NHkbj2cjt3Wy8u--yL-vYv2.jpeg" type="image/jpeg"><img referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.jellow.site/Fmhf8Y8NHkbj2cjt3Wy8u--yL-vYv2.jpeg"></picture><br><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FozeoUDc59Sxyc_E-IxaeNEDcc0-v2.jpeg/strip/format/webp" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FozeoUDc59Sxyc_E-IxaeNEDcc0-v2.jpeg" type="image/jpeg"><img referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.jellow.site/FozeoUDc59Sxyc_E-IxaeNEDcc0-v2.jpeg"></picture><br><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FhooNvqNo81mP3a0eNiQg0j2HT-1v2.jpeg/strip/format/webp" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FhooNvqNo81mP3a0eNiQg0j2HT-1v2.jpeg" type="image/jpeg"><img referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.jellow.site/FhooNvqNo81mP3a0eNiQg0j2HT-1v2.jpeg"></picture><br><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FmFnNAysNTH-yIUHK-hFs6lBItvYv2.jpeg/strip/format/webp" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/FmFnNAysNTH-yIUHK-hFs6lBItvYv2.jpeg" type="image/jpeg"><img referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.jellow.site/FmFnNAysNTH-yIUHK-hFs6lBItvYv2.jpeg"></picture><br><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/Fgpf5i_ft7bzwrj4t7AkiSgfB_-wv2.jpeg/strip/format/webp" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/Fgpf5i_ft7bzwrj4t7AkiSgfB_-wv2.jpeg" type="image/jpeg"><img referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.jellow.site/Fgpf5i_ft7bzwrj4t7AkiSgfB_-wv2.jpeg"></picture>]]></description>
